main event: Witness observed 5 bright oblong-shaped yellow objects proceeding in formation at a high rate of speed.
interesting points: The objects were estimated to be traveling at approximately 600-700 mph.,The sighting lasted about 3-4 minutes.,Witness initially thought it could be flashing lights reflecting off clouds but felt the phenomena was unexplainable.,No known aircraft or astronomical objects were present in the area at the time.,The event was recorded in a Project Blue Book report.
witness description: The witness observed the objects from their backyard window.
